And next thing you
know, it's going viral.

00:33:20.200 --> 00:33:21.570
I see it on the actual news.

00:33:21.570 --> 00:33:25.070
I see it on ESPN and, you know--

00:33:25.070 --> 00:33:28.310
and some Nebraska fans were
